Package xyz.swatt.data_mapping_validator

This package contains helper classes for validating data being mapped from one location and/or format to another, typically through a process like a workflow.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataMapping
    This interface is for all Data Mapping Classes that compare 2 values of the same type.
    DataMapping.DataMappingFlagEnum
    Every Implementing Class should have a "Column" enum than implements this interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BigDecimalMapping
    Use this class to validate that 2 different BigDecimals, Doubles, or Floats are equivalent.
    CollectionMapping<T>
    Use this class to validate that 2 different Collections of Objects are equal, By using the Object's build in equals(Object) method.
    LocalDateTimeMapping
    Use this class to validate that 2 different LocalDateTimes, LocalDates, LocalTimes, ZonedDateTimes, or Strings Representing Date and/or Time are equal.
    LongMapping
    Use this class to validate that 2 different Longs, Integers, or Shorts are equivalent.
    ObjectMapping<T>
    Use this class to validate that 2 different Ts are equal.
    SqlPojoCollectionMapping<T>
    Use this class to validate that 2 different Collections of SqlPojos are equal, compareing their Column Values.
    SqlPojoMapping<T extends DataMapping>
    Use this class to validate that two different Columns in two different SqlPojos are equal.
    StringMapping
    Use this class to validate that 2 different Strings or Characters are equal.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BigDecimalMapping.MappingFlag
    List of possible flags for a Data Mapping.
    CollectionMapping.MappingFlag
    List of possible flags for a Data Mapping.
    LocalDateTimeMapping.MappingFlag
    List of possible flags for a Data Mapping.
    StringMapping.MappingFlag
    List of possible flags for a Data Mapping.
